                <div class="hero">
                    <h1 class="hero-title">The Adriatic Advantage</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">Albania's BPO firms have proved that nearshoring need not mean compromise</p>
                    <a href="#" class="hero-cta" onclick="navigateToPage(1); return false;">Read the Story</a>
                </div>
